Title

create_file.Rd

Title

Usage

create_file(n_pat, n_samp)

Arguments

n_pat

Number of patients

n_samp

Number of samples

Value

A vector of file names

Examples

n_pat <- 3
n_samp <- 3
create_file(n_pat,n_samp)
#>  [1] "data_patient_1_sample_1.fastq" "data_patient_1_sample_2.fastq"
#>  [3] "data_patient_1_sample_3.fastq" "data_patient_2_sample_1.fastq"

#>  [7] "data_patient_3_sample_1.fastq" "data_patient_3_sample_2.fastq"

#> [11] "data_patient_1_sample_2.cram"  "data_patient_1_sample_3.cram"

#> [17] "data_patient_3_sample_2.cram"  "data_patient_3_sample_3.cram" 
#> [19] "data_patient_1_sample_1.vcf"   "data_patient_1_sample_2.vcf"  
#> [21] "data_patient_1_sample_3.vcf"   "data_patient_2_sample_1.vcf"

#> [25] "data_patient_3_sample_1.vcf"   "data_patient_3_sample_2.vcf"
